76561198059876777,Recommended,628420,31521230,Posted: 3 May,all,Satans Little Helper,"Die,die,die...die,die and die hundreds of times again, NGHTMN is a platformer game that makes the player do a lot of trial and error .  The game has 30 fairly small levels but what it lacks in length it compensates with lots of traps, spikes and particular chain saw blades. The  handling of the protagonist is done with the arrow keys and the spacebar and at times it adds to the challenge as lots of the jumps and movement demands precision. The game has 489 achievements that all is doable if the player has a bit of patience and has some previous experience with platformers. At the cost of 0,99 euro ill deffently recommend the game as i had a few hours of fun playing it. I'll rate it at 6/10."
